metadata.name: Moby Caricature - Moby X Prasad Bhat
metadata.description:
This is a special collaboration with @prasadbhatart!

This is a remix'd version of MobyHead #1 (The Original). Thank you so much Prasad for this truly one of a kind piece. It's a true honor. ❤️
